9 SECTION 3. All actions taken at a remote or hybrid town meeting held in accordance
10 with this act shall be ratified, validated and confirmed to the same extent as if the town meeting
11 had been conducted entirely in person.
12 SECTION 4. This act shall take effect upon its passage.
